      <title>莫桑比克当选总统希望在动乱后恢复投资者信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/president-elect-chapo-plans-dialog-to-end-mozambique-unrest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克新任总统丹尼尔·查波计划举行民族和解谈判，以解决不断升级的政治危机，该危机已导致数十人死亡，并导致这个天然气资源丰富的国家经济增长停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/president-elect-chapo-plans-dialog-to-end-mozambique-unrest</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 09:09:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关键过境协议仅剩一周，欧洲天然气价格波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/european-gas-extends-gains-with-one-week-left-on-transit-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于持续的供应担忧，欧洲天然气价格在每兆瓦时 45 欧元以上波动，而距离俄罗斯和乌克兰之间的一项重要过境协议仅剩一周时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/european-gas-extends-gains-with-one-week-left-on-transit-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 08:03:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
